<plot>This Promo Video introduces the story of "Lundon's Bridge and the Three Keys" to American students. It shows that an 8 year-old little girl and a 15 year-old boy use the magic of love and belief in their parents to win the war between the land and the sea. Lundon (the little girl) and Waxer (the teenage boy) end up on many magical adventures during their quest to save the world from pollution. A dolphin turns into a beach bum and a jellyfish queen turns into a human fairy godmother.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?243241</url></doc>
